Description: Papyrus fragment with 7 lines of Coptic text written along the fibres (recto), 1 line on reverse written against the fibres (verso). EA 75337, 75336, 75335, 75334 are mounted together.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380761) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380761)
